   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Training Barbados youth in farming and leadership</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In our experiential educational programming, we seek the holistic development of the youth we engage. Using a Science, Technology, Engineering, Arts and Mathematics (STEAM) curriculum on an agricultural platform, our aim is to create change agents empowered to lead and transform their own communities. Working in organic farming environments, youth will be exposed to food production, agro-processing, natural building, culinary arts, video production, bookkeeping and lots of exciting activities.</narrative>
  </description>
